name: Journyx
overview:
Journyx, Inc. develops Web-based time, expense, and project tracking solutions. Its solutions include Timesheet, a timesheet and expense management solution that enables to manage employee timesheets and expenses for project control, customer invoicing, and payroll automation; and ProjectXecute that provides project resource management and actual work reporting, billable time reporting, a central repository for project and resource data, material and reimbursable expense tracking, project cost accounting, status reporting, and overhead and leave tracking. The company also provides installation assistance, system integration, project management, training, and technical support services, as well as application hosting services. Its solutions enable customers to gather and analyze information for per person/per project profitability.

The company was founded in 1996 and is based in Austin, Texas.
